<H2>Description Tab</H2>
<P>This tab is used to enter the description into the control record.</P>

<TABLE>
 <TR>
  <TH>Field</TH>
  <TH>Description</TH>
 <TR>
<TR>
 <TD>Summary</TD>
 <TD>This is a summary of package and should be kept short as it is displayed in the main Package Managers window. PackIt forces a Maximum of 80 characters.</TD>
</TR>
<TR>
 <TD>Description</TD>
 <TD>This is the full description of the package.</TD>
</TR>
</TABLE>

